208
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:32,000
Milk tea powder.

209
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:32,640
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

210
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:37,440
Top-quality milk tea powder.

211
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,320
