271
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,200
Boss, it's a misunderstanding.

272
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:55,560
It really is a misunderstanding!

273
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:57,960
A complete misunderstanding.

274
00:13:58,520 --> 00:13:59,480
It's really not what you think.

275
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,480
A total misunderstanding!

276
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:02,360
Savior!
